translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  2,154,"Ni ngasim'bechetaga pa kwamba ya ŵandu ŵaakuwulajidwa petala lya Allah kuti: “Ŵawe.” Nambo ŵachijumi gamba kuti ngankupata kumanyilila"
  2,155,"Soni chitun'dinje ni chindu chakogoya (mpela ngondo), kwisa soni sala, kunandipa kwa ipanje, kwasika kwa maumi ni konasika kwa isogosi, ni mwatagulilani ŵakupilila abali jakusengwasya"
  2,156,"Aŵala ŵanti naga ipato yapatilemo akasatiji: “Chisimu uwwe ŵa Allah, soni chisimu uwwe Kukwakwe tuuchiujila.”"
  2,157,"Ŵanganyao ukoto wakuumila kwa M’mbuje gwao uli pa jamanjao ni chanasa, soni ŵanyao niŵali ŵakongoka"
  2,158,"Chisimu (matumbi ga) Swafa ni Maruwa gaŵele mu imanyilo ya (Dini ja) Allah, sano jwalijose jwapite kutenda Hija kapena Umra, paŵe pangali ulemwa kwa jwalakwejo kuusyausya kwenda chilikati chakwecho, mwanti jwachapanganye masengo mwa gamba kulipeleka (nikuti tachilipidwa), chisimu Allah ni Jwakutogolela kusyene, Jwakumanyilila nnope"
  2,159,"Chisimu aŵala ŵaakusisa yatutulwisye yaili ilosyo yakuonechela palangulangu soni yaili chongoko, panyuma panti tuisalichisye kwa ŵandu m’Chitabu, ŵanganyao niŵaakuŵa ali nkulwesedwa ni Allah, soni ni akuŵa ali nkulwesedwa ni akulwesa"
  2,160,"Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵatesile toba ni kwilanya (yaŵawatanganyagayo) ni kusalichisya (yaŵasisagayo), basi ŵanganyao ni ŵachinapochele toba jao, soni Une ni Jwakupochela nnope toba, Jwachanasa channope"
  2,161,"Chisimu aŵala ŵakanile nikwikanila kuwa ali makafili, ŵanganyao malweso ga Allah, Achimalaika ni ŵandu wosope gali pa jamanjao"
  2,162,"Mwele (mmalweso ga ku Motogo) chakaŵe ŵandamo, ilagasyo ngaija kupungusyidwa kwa jamanjao, soni ŵanyao ngaaja kupedwa lipesa"
  2,163,"Soni Nnungu jwenu ni Nnungu Jumpepe basi, pangali nnungu jwine (jwakuŵajilwa kun'galagatila) ikaŵeje Jwelepejo, Jwaukoto wejinji, Jwachanasa channope"